@{
    
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>الصفحة الرئيسية</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1321 0%, #1D2D44 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .bg-animation {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .bg-circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.08;
            animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

            .bg-circle:nth-child(1) {
                width: 400px;
                height: 400px;
                background: #748CAB;
                top: -100px;
                right: -100px;
                animation-delay: 0s;
            }

            .bg-circle:nth-child(2) {
                width: 300px;
                height: 300px;
                background: #3E5C76;
                bottom: -80px;
                left: -80px;
                animation-delay: 5s;
            }

            .bg-circle:nth-child(3) {
                width: 250px;
                height: 250px;
                background: #F0EBD8;
                top: 50%;
                left: 50%;
                animation-delay: 10s;
            }

        @@keyframes float {
            0%, 100%

        {
            transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
        }

        33% {
            transform: translate(50px, -50px) scale(1.1);
        }

        66% {
            transform: translate(-30px, 30px) scale(0.9);
        }

        }

        .navbar {
            background: rgba(29, 45, 68, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240, 235, 216, 0.1);
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .navbar-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            color: #F0EBD8;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
            color: #F0EBD8;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.5);
            display: inline-block;
        }

            .nav-btn:hover {
                background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.4);
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
            }

        .main-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .cards-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; /* نص ونص */
            gap: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 80vh; /* خليها تقريبا 80% من الشاشة */
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(29, 45, 68, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(240, 235, 216, 0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: slideIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @@keyframes slideIn {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3E5C76 0%, #748CAB 50%, #3E5C76 100%);
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes shimmer {
            0%

        {
            background-position: 0% 50%;
        }

        50% {
            background-position: 100% 50%;
        }

        100% {
            background-position: 0% 50%;
        }

        }

        .image-card {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

        .profile-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

        /* كارد البيانات */
        .data-card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden; /* يشيل السكروول */
        }

            .data-card::-webkit-scrollbar {
                display: none;
            }

           

            .data-card::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
                background: rgba(240, 235, 216, 0.05);
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .data-card::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
                background: rgba(240, 235, 216, 0.2);
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

        .profile-header {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }

        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        }

        .profile-name {
            color: #F0EBD8;
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .profile-title {
            color: #748CAB;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .profile-location {
            color: #3E5C76;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

            .profile-location::before {
                content: '📍 ';
            }

        .divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #748CAB, transparent);
            margin: 40px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }

        .about-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.5s both;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #F0EBD8;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text {
            color: #748CAB;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .social-section {
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 50px; /* المسافة بين الأيقونات */
            margin-top: 25px;
            flex-wrap: wrap; /* عشان لو الشاشة صغيرة الأيقونات تنزل سطر */
        }

        .social-link {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #F0EBD8;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border: 2px solid #748CAB;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(62, 92, 118, 0.1);
        }

        .social-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #F0EBD8;
        }

        .social-link:hover .social-icon {
            background: #748CAB;
            color: #0D1321;
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(116, 140, 171, 0.6);
        }


        /* تصميم متجاوب */
        @@media (max-width: 1200px) {
            .cards-wrapper

        {
            grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
            height: auto;
        }

        }

        @@media (max-width: 992px) {
            .cards-wrapper

        {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            height: auto;
        }

        .image-card {
            height: 500px;
        }

        .data-card {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        }

        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar-container

        {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .main-container {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .image-card,
        .data-card {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .profile-name {
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        .profile-title {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .social-links {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-animation">
        <div class="bg-circle"></div>
        <div class="bg-circle"></div>
        <div class="bg-circle"></div>
    </div>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-container">
            <div class="navbar-brand"><i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i> الصفحة الرئيسية</div>
            <a href="#" class="nav-btn"> تسجيل الخروج <i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i></a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="cards-wrapper">


            <!-- كارد البيانات -->
            <div class="card data-card">
                <div class="profile-header">
                    <h1 class="profile-name">أحمد حمدان</h1>
                    <p class="profile-title">مهندس برمجيات</p>
                    <p class="profile-location">دبي، الإمارات العربية المتحدة</p>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div class="about-section">
                    <h3 class="section-title">نبذة عني</h3>
                    <p class="about-text">
                        مهندس برمجيات متخصص في تطوير تطبيقات الويب باستخدام أحدث التقنيات.
                        أمتلك خبرة واسعة في بناء حلول برمجية مبتكرة وفعالة تساعد الشركات على تحقيق أهدافها الرقمية.
                        شغوف بالتعلم المستمر ومواكبة أحدث التطورات في عالم التكنولوجيا والبرمجة.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="social-section">
                    <h3 class="section-title">تواصل معي</h3>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                            <span class="social-icon"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i></span>
                            <span class="social-text">فيسبوك</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                            <span class="social-icon"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"></i></span>
                            <span class="social-text">لينكد إن</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                            <span class="social-icon"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></span>
                            <span class="social-text">يوتيوب</span>
                        </a>
                        @* <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                            <span class="social-icon">💾</span>
                            <span class="social-text">جيتهاب</span>
                        </a> *@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- كارد الصورة -->
            <div class="card image-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=400&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Ahmed Hamdan" class="profile-image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>